<body>

    <h1>AI Responsibility Act</h1>

    <h2>What problem does it solve?</h2>
    <p>This law addresses the lack of accountability when AI systems cause harm.</p>

    <h2>Main Rules</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Companies must test AI for safety</li>
        <li>AI decisions must be explainable</li>
        <li>Developers are responsible for damages</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who Benefits?</h2>
    <p>Citizens, workers, and businesses that rely on safe AI systems.</p>

    <h2>Possible Criticisms</h2>
    <p>Some argue it could slow innovation and increase costs.</p>

    <h2>Why Voters Should Support It</h2>
    <p>This law ensures AI is used responsibly and protects society.</p>

